rows.label: tlk43300241_03_msg0001
rows.name: The state of the world keeps changing.

rows.label: tlk43300241_03_msg0002
rows.name:
Seeing the lives of the commoners from
here, and painting the scenes I see, I
think I can understand it clearly.

rows.label: tlk43300241_03_msg0003
rows.name:
Unlike my father, who's
involved in the government,
or the other nobles...

rows.label: tlk43300241_03_msg0004
rows.name:
Oh, they can talk about the
Superbian treaty, or the
reparations, for days...

rows.label: tlk43300241_03_msg0005
rows.name:
But they don't hear the word
on the street like I do.
